import { useState } from 'react'; import React from 'react' import { Link, useHistory } from 'react-router-dom'; import { ToastContainer, toast } from 'react-toastify'; import 'react-toastify/dist/ReactToastify.css'; import Header from '../partials/Header'; import { useAuth } from '../context/AuthContext'; function SignIn() { const history = useHistory() const [email, setEmail] = useState('') const [password, setPassword]= useState ('') const [isSubmitting, setIsSubmitting] = useState (false) const [error, setError] = useState("") const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false) const {login, signInWithGoogle}= useAuth() async function handleSubmit(e) { e.preventDefault() if(!email || !password){ toast.error("Credentials not Valid") } setIsSubmitting(true) login(email, password).then(response=>{ console.log(response) history.push('/dashboard') toast.success("Sucessfully login") }).catch(error=>{ console.log(error.code) toast.error(error.code) if(error.code === 'auth/wrong-password'){ toast.error('Please check the Password'); } if(error.code === 'auth/user-not-found'){ toast.error('Please check the Email'); } }).finally(()=>setIsSubmitting(false)) setLoading(false) } return (
